{"tid":404832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持報警L]曾樹和笠水cut記者線 牧師感不安報警冀阻歪風","createTime":"2017-09-18T11:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T11:58:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c65ed848a5655f49ffb04e073b2d2db549e71065","tid":404832,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170918/57225734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170918%2F57225734&d=4ZXabHcFZBev3dktCAp0NDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=82f0acfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170918%2F57225734&h=3f99f881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170918/57225734</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯昨在添馬公園舉行的「革走戴耀廷吶喊大會」，有份出席的屏山鄉鄉事委員會主席曾樹和曾大叫口號「搞港獨者必須要殺！」，並由何君堯附和高呼「無赦」。《蘋果》今天就事件聯絡曾樹和回應，而他未等及記者提出問題，即表示：「我唔發表&hellip;&hellip;我唔發表任何嘢，OK？」，隨即掛斷電話。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午有市民稱因對該番「港獨殺無赦」言論深感不安，而決定到灣仔警署總部報警。報案人士表示，望警方能嚴正執法，阻止仇恨言語歪風，全力徹查事件，保障香港市民安全。報警者之一的牧師劉先生，質疑言論涉嫌觸犯香港法例第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第5條串謀或唆使謀殺，認為局方必須正視問題嚴重性，避免社會出現暴力事件。"},{"pid":"9c1682aea4c03bc3157a3c977ae82dd8e98321d2","tid":404832,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e9421737b57e598ed93fdd511fc7c930065dee1","tid":404832,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee01222c44bbf79fa9fdf5645eec74a3dc17ff10","tid":404832,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"一齊報警啦 好驚"},{"pid":"0f9389b91257d987bd2669b0a0b65de859278a9c","tid":404832,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"大佬叫收聲？唔係好撚威咩？"},{"pid":"5ce4465a135e7d5e1c4ed8bab89a